    dc:date "2017" ;
    dc:title "New Siberian “ spineless ” species of Thalassaphorura Bagnall, 1949 (Collembola, Onychiuridae), with a key to world species of the genus" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1084042>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1084054>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1084046>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1084044> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1084042>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–8. Thalassaphorura aspinata sp. nov.: 1, habitus and dorsal chaetotaxy; 2, dorsal side of Ant. III and IV; 3, AIIIO; 4, PAO and anterior cephalic pso; 5, tibiotarsal chaetotaxy and claw of leg III; 6, chaetotaxy of anal valves; 7, shape of S-chaetaeand modified chaetae of MVO(a‒‒Th.tergaII‒III,b‒‒Sl chaetaonAbd.terga I‒III,c‒‒Sp chaetaon Abd.tergum V, d‒‒modified chaetae of MVO); 8, chaetotaxy of Abd.sterna I‒VI." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1084042/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1084054>
    dc:description "FIGURES45–52. Chaetotaxy of Abd. tergum VI (dorsal and lateral view): 45‒46, Thalassaphorura macrospinata Sun & Wu, 2012 from Russia (Far East); 47‒48, Thalassaphorura zschokkei (Handschin,1919) from Iran; 49‒50, Thalassaphorura tovtrensis (Kaprus’ & Weiner, 1994) from Ukraine; 51, Thalassaphorura aspinata sp. nov.: chaetotaxy of Abd. tergum V and VI; 52, Thalassaphorura sibirica sp. nov.: chaetotaxy of labium." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1084054/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1084046>
    dc:description "FIGURES 16–23. Thalassaphorura sibirica sp. nov: 16, habitus and dorsal chaetotaxy; 17, dorsal side of Ant. III and IV; 18, sensory rods and sensory clubs of AIIIO; 19, maxillary palp, 20, PAO and anterior cephalic pso; 21, tibiotarsal chaetotaxy and claw of leg III; 22, shape of S-chaetae (a‒‒Th. terga II‒III, b‒‒Sl chaeta on Abd. terga I‒III, c‒‒Sp chaeta on Abd. tergum V); 23, chaetotaxy of Abd.sterna I‒VI." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1084046/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1084044>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9–15. Thalassaphorura sayana sp. nov.: 9, habitus and dorsal chaetotaxy; 10, dorsal side of Ant. III and IV; 11, chaetotaxy of labium; 12, Ptibiotarsal chaetotaxy and claw of leg III; 13, PAO and anterior cephalic psoI; 14, shape of Schaetae (a‒‒Th. terga II‒III, b‒‒Sl chaeta on Abd. terga I‒III, c‒‒Sp chaeta on Abd. tergum V, d‒‒S chaeta on Abd. tergum VI); 15, chaetotaxy of Abd. sterna I‒VI." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1084044/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

